clearScanDisplay(25.10)                                clearScanDisplay(25.10)

Name
       clearScanDisplay - Removes scan chains from the display

Syntax
       clearScanDisplay

       [-help]

       [<chain_name>]

       Removes scan chains from the display.

Parameters
       <chain_name>
              Specifies the scan chain to remove from the display.

              Default: Removes all scan chains from the display.

Related Information
              * Placing the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

                     * Optimizing and Reordering Scan Chains

